title: Water Overflow
description: “Oh, crazy..!! That’s wearing or naked!?” Swimming pool Alba suddenly came to the request of an acquaintance. Byung-jin, who knew how to make her eyes stand out with the dizzying women’s swimming clothes, accidentally suffers from a major accident in which she tears the swimsuit of her first love, Da-hee. Water starts leaking in the homeroom due to the overturning, and at the owner’s house, who has decided to stay during the repair period, he encounters familiar swimming pool girls…
